256
00:17:05,880 --> 00:17:07,640
I've got a bunch of books and I'm reading them.

257
00:17:07,640 --> 00:17:10,660
I'm getting all kinds of different opinions about what the gifts are.

258
00:17:12,120 --> 00:17:13,740
That's a little frustrating sometimes.

259
00:17:15,320 --> 00:17:21,320
I've come to realize that I think the Scripture is giving these overviews of the gifts,

260
00:17:21,320 --> 00:17:26,020
and there may be a few more that he does use at times that may not be listed specifically.

261
00:17:27,270 --> 00:17:29,390
But I don't want to be too dogmatic on that either.

262
00:17:29,610 --> 00:17:30,690
I'm not totally sure.

263
00:17:30,950 --> 00:17:35,270
But what I do know is the ones that we're going to list, I believe, are scripturally based,

264
00:17:35,330 --> 00:17:36,770
and I've seen them in experience.

