322
00:21:18,640 --> 00:21:28,480
The giving gift is not just a challenge for us to be givers to the Lord of what the Bible clearly says we should be giving as tithing people.

323
00:21:29,100 --> 00:21:38,980
The gift of giving is for those who have a special gift and ability from God to give way more than is required.

324
00:21:39,540 --> 00:21:44,280
It's to go well above and beyond, say, a 10% of our giving.

325
00:21:44,280 --> 00:21:50,780
It's to really get out there and give third, a half, 90% away.

326
00:21:53,420 --> 00:21:54,220
