And I give to the Lord.

331
00:22:05,130 --> 00:22:06,070
I give plenty away.

332
00:22:06,410 --> 00:22:11,570
But let's be honest, I still like things and I like to use things and buy things and so forth.

333
00:22:11,710 --> 00:22:13,750
