335
00:22:24,670 --> 00:22:32,270
That's where they are most deeply fulfilled is when they're giving away what God has blessed them with for his kingdom.

336
00:22:33,290 --> 00:22:36,070
And they just love to give it away.

337
00:22:39,620 --> 00:22:46,760
The challenging part is if you have the gift of giving, it's easy to project that on everybody else and somehow look down at everybody else if you don't do that.

338
00:22:46,760 --> 00:22:48,740
That's a danger with any of the gifts.

339
00:22:49,740 --> 00:22:52,380
But if you've got the special gift of giving, praise the Lord.

340
00:22:53,880 --> 00:22:57,950
And you need to exercise that and work with it.

341
00:23:00,940 --> 00:23:04,840
It's the ability to give a significant percentage beyond the tithe to the kingdom.

342
00:23:06,110 --> 00:23:09,790
If you have that gift, and I know some of you do,

