348
00:23:36,940 --> 00:23:39,460
You can see how powerful that gift is in the church.

349
00:23:41,100 --> 00:23:45,750
You do realize that Jesus was bankrolled in his ministry by women.

350
00:23:46,190 --> 00:23:48,390
Many of them perhaps had the spiritual gift of giving,

351
00:23:48,530 --> 00:23:53,370
for they gave liberally that he might have a ministry.

352
00:23:53,790 --> 00:23:56,650
It's a powerful gift.

353
00:23:56,650 --> 00:24:06,620
the gift of giving. The second one is the gift of hospitality. This gift allows people with great

