442
00:29:44,030 --> 00:29:46,530
You are to be used in the church and foreign missions.

443
00:29:47,660 --> 00:29:49,700
Ministry locally to the underprivileged.

444
00:29:50,630 --> 00:29:53,050
Perhaps ministry to the homeless and the refugees.

445
00:29:54,540 --> 00:29:56,640
And do community outreach and things like that.

446
00:29:57,740 --> 00:30:02,240
This is a tough one today in this world of incredible consumerism.

