455
00:30:48,040 --> 00:30:51,180
Oftentimes, people with this gift also have the gift of teaching.

456
00:30:51,720 --> 00:30:54,020
Those two often go hand in hand, and that makes sense.

457
00:30:54,920 --> 00:31:01,220
If you have this gift of knowledge, you are interested in the ideas of moving towards the healthy church in North America.

458
00:31:01,780 --> 00:31:03,840
And what does it take to move to those directions?

459
00:31:03,840 --> 00:31:16,300
You are involved in church growth research, in presenting seminars, in writing, in long-term planning, in Bible study, theological studies,

460
00:31:17,710 --> 00:31:20,710
creative outreach opportunities, things like that.

461
00:31:21,600 --> 00:31:22,600
You have the gift of knowledge.

462
00:31:25,680 --> 00:31:29,960
You just enjoy the ideas in terms of developing the kingdom.

463
00:31:30,680 --> 00:31:34,800
And you have the ability to analyze and bring those together

464
00:31:34,800 --> 00:31:39,140
and share them in a way that's persuasive and encouraging to others.

465
00:31:39,240 --> 00:31:42,920
And you build the kingdom through harnessing these ideas.

466
00:31:43,660 --> 00:31:46,740
It's a great, wonderful gift, as they all are.

467
00:31:47,830 --> 00:31:50,030
And some of you have that gift in this room.

468
00:31:52,810 --> 00:32:01,400
