470
00:32:10,240 --> 00:32:15,850
The original word, as I looked at that, had to do with steering and piloting a ship.

471
00:32:16,930 --> 00:32:20,570
The captain usually made the decision of where we were going as a general rule.

472
00:32:20,570 --> 00:32:21,770
This is the direction.

473
00:32:22,150 --> 00:32:26,970
