475
00:32:32,370 --> 00:32:37,860
They can organize and set things together and make it effective.

476
00:32:40,570 --> 00:32:42,050
I don't think I have this gift.

477
00:32:43,530 --> 00:32:44,610
And if you have it, I need you.

478
00:32:45,610 --> 00:32:46,770
That's how the body works together.

479
00:32:51,130 --> 00:32:51,490
Wisdom.

