488
00:33:33,300 --> 00:33:36,420
in training courses, in gift consulting.

489
00:33:37,080 --> 00:33:38,320
It's a big area for us.

490
00:33:39,420 --> 00:33:43,800
As we process, if you will, people and learn what their gifts are

