00:33:43,800 --> 00:33:45,920
and work them through to help them discern these gifts,

492
00:33:45,920 --> 00:33:50,200
we need people who have the gift of wisdom that can sit down with you

493
00:33:50,200 --> 00:33:54,920
and hear your story and see what it says on the list

494
00:33:54,920 --> 00:33:57,540
