495
00:33:57,540 --> 00:33:58,760
and where you can be used.

496
00:33:59,630 --> 00:34:02,010
The gift of wisdom allows you to help in that process.

497
00:34:05,770 --> 00:34:08,110
It should be used in seminars and church consulting

498
00:34:08,110 --> 00:34:09,530
and all kinds of things like that.

499
00:34:11,870 --> 00:34:12,670
It's the gift of wisdom.

