The first one here, under creative potential,

513
00:34:49,900 --> 00:34:53,970
as a subtext, subheading, is this one.

514
00:34:53,970 --> 00:34:56,730
The gift of artistic creativity.

515
00:34:56,730 --> 00:35:05,050
Exodus 31, 2 Samuel 6, 1 Kings 7

516
00:35:05,050 --> 00:35:09,490
