517
00:35:09,490 --> 00:35:14,040
This gift enables Christians to use artistic expression

518
00:35:14,040 --> 00:35:17,880
For the building up of others in the church

519
00:35:17,880 --> 00:35:20,800
Through artistic expression

520
00:35:20,800 --> 00:35:24,860
You bless others and build up their faith in some way

