00:36:08,040 --> 00:36:10,520
The more I think about it and talk to people,

530
00:36:10,620 --> 00:36:13,800
I think this gift really does operate in the church today.

531
00:36:16,120 --> 00:36:19,980
The second one on these last three is the gift of craftsmanship.

532
00:36:23,020 --> 00:36:27,180
Exodus 30, 2 Kings 12, 2 Chronicles 34, Acts 18.

533
00:36:27,680 --> 00:36:32,480
