535
00:36:40,450 --> 00:36:43,690
Many of you are wonderful, gifted people with your hands.

536
00:36:46,100 --> 00:36:49,700
And I really thank God for what you've done, not only in my life, but in the life of this church,

537
00:36:49,840 --> 00:36:52,360
