538
00:36:52,840 --> 00:36:57,060
Many of you have trades and gifts with your hands.

539
00:36:57,820 --> 00:36:59,920
If you have a spiritual gift of craftsmanship,

540
00:36:59,920 --> 00:37:04,880
you are truly blessed, more than anything else, in using those gifts for the church.

541
00:37:07,270 --> 00:37:07,890
You see the difference?

542
00:37:08,010 --> 00:37:11,410
It has to do with building up the body of Christ is where that gift takes off.

543
00:37:17,090 --> 00:37:22,540
