549
00:37:53,680 --> 00:37:57,000
for the glory of God and the edification of others.

550
00:37:59,420 --> 00:38:02,420
Some people sing with a beautiful voice.

551
00:38:02,660 --> 00:38:04,000
Others sing with a beautiful voice

552
00:38:04,000 --> 00:38:06,560
and God uses that voice to touch your life

553
00:38:06,560 --> 00:38:08,640
