557
00:38:16,900 --> 00:38:17,940
That'd be the gift of music.

558
00:38:19,120 --> 00:38:23,840
1 Samuel chapter 16, 1 Corinthians 14.

559
00:38:25,740 --> 00:38:28,880
Colossians 3 seemed to point to that gift.

560
00:38:29,910 --> 00:38:34,330
And if you have that gift, worship leading, instrumentalist, worship team,

561
00:38:34,950 --> 00:38:38,450
street outreach, choir member, vocal soloist, those things,

562
00:38:38,450 --> 00:38:43,450
