00:38:55,110 --> 00:38:58,670
In a couple of weeks, you're going to have an opportunity to really discern that.

565
00:38:59,460 --> 00:39:02,120
October 6th will be an important day for the life of our church here.

566
00:39:02,260 --> 00:39:03,080
You won't want to miss it.

